    E01 A Leap
    29 Feb 2024

    29 Feb 2024

    Description

    With an IQ of 242, Antonia Scott becomes the "Red Queen" of a secret, experimental police project. Together with Jon, a temperamental Basque policeman, she becomes involved in a twisted game of cat and mouse.
